    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know, i know... i've heard the helpline thing a million times. it doesn't change the fact that i'm failing everything and just feel like a complete waste of space. it's like no matter how hard i try, there's no way out of this cycle. everything just feels so pointless.",
